<div id="c11">
<p>&#8220;vast majority of Groupon’s marketing budget was spent marketing TO BUSINESSES&#8221;</p>

<p>False. Its marketing costs are almost exclusively related to building its email list and account base. It&#8217;s sales efforts are included in SG&amp;A.</p>

<p>So, yes, Groupon could bring marketing spend to $0 and still run an effective business.</p>

